      <hedline>
        <hl1>Russia Says It Halted Attacks in Chechnya</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The Russian military said it had suspended airstrikes and artillery attacks in the breakaway region of Chechnya, a move clearly intended to build support for Moscow's newly appointed administrator there.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>The Russian military said it had suspended airstrikes and artillery attacks in the breakaway region of Chechnya, a move clearly intended to build support for Moscow's newly appointed administrator there.</p>
        <p>Russia has repeatedly claimed to have broken the rebel resistance, though fighting has continued. There was little expectation that the fighting, which has caused countless casualties, would end now.</p>
        <p>Article, Page A5.</p>
      </block>
